abstracts.cdata!:
The proposed project consists of
            dredging at the ports of La Goulette (Tunis), Bizerte,
            Menzel-Bourguiba and Sfax; provision of a dredger and
            attendant tug for maintenance dredging; replacement of
            cargo-handling equipment, provision of additional equipment
            and rehabilitation of quay cranes; reconstruction of the
            island breakwater at Bizerte; construction of an additional
            berth to handle bulk cereals, with a bulk grain storage silo
            and associated handling equipment; training of a financial
            manager and other senior staff; and the provision of
            accounting and engineering consultants.
